&lt;DIV&gt;Organics/ Wolfblade:&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;Organics came online after some time in the CR chamber.&nbsp; She stepped out and examined her body, now shiny.&nbsp; She decided she wanted to get something to drink and headed for the mess hall.&nbsp; On the way there, she heard sobbing and cying.&nbsp; She followed the noise to the lab where Wolfblade and Kup sat.&nbsp; Upon seeing Wolfblade in her moment of sadness, the valkyrie instantly knew why she greived.&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&quot;Wolfblade, would you come with me to the dining room?&nbsp; I want to explain something.&quot;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;The sobbing female stopped crying and looked up at the valkyrie.&nbsp; Tears streamed from the corners of her optics, but she stood and followed Organics.&nbsp; They ntered the dining room and Wolfblade collapsed in a chair.&nbsp; Organics got them both a glass of enegon, and sat next to the smaller femme.&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&quot;I understand you greive, I wish he was still here too, but it&#39;s not a lost cause.&quot;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&quot;What?&quot; Wolfblade asked,&quot;you mean, he did go and join them, like Kup said?&quot;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;Organics was a little suprised Kup told her Malice joined the Minions volentarily, but dismissed it.&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&quot;No.&nbsp; In fact, he fought with such a feriocity, any Decepticon would cower befoe him.&nbsp; They would come and come, and he continued to throw them aside.&nbsp; But he got too tired, they finally swarmed him, and captured him.&nbsp; They ran away after that, he broke their will to fight, he fought well-&quot;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&quot;SHUT UP!&quot; Wolfblade yelled, standing suddenly and slamming her fists into the table.&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&quot;HE&#39;S NOT DEAD!&nbsp; STOP TALKING ABOUT HIM LIKE HE&#39;S DEAD!&quot;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;Organics kept the cool exterior, and stood to comfort the smaller bot.&nbsp; Wolfblade broke into sobs again, and leaned against Organics.&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&quot;I&#39;m sorry, I didn&#39;t mean it like that,&quot; Organics said, holding Wolfblade by the shoulders,&quot;we&#39;ll get him back, Rodimus and the others are already working on a plan to gt him back.&nbsp; Please keep faith in the others, we&#39;ll get Malice back, don&#39;t worry.&quot;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;Wolfblade stopped sniffling and took a few deep breaths.&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&quot;Alright, thank you Organics.&nbsp; Just don&#39;t tell anyone about this,&quot; she said, laughing a little.&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;Organics laughed a litle and sat back down.&nbsp; Wolfblade sat also and both femmes drank the energon.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@...&gt;&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt; wrote:&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE class=replbq style=&quot;PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px; BORDER-LEFT: #1010ff 2px solid&quot;&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;: : Kup : :&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Kup looked up, his optics now focusing on the femme. He saw the pain she was going through and watching it hurt him.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;He walks closer to her, resting his left hand on her right shoulder.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Kup: &lt;/STRONG&gt;Only he knows why he did what he did. I&#39;m so sorry for your loss...&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;At this point he was really at a loss for words.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;Yojinbo of Nightmare &lt;bustercross365@...&gt;&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt; wrote:&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE class=replbq style=&quot;PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px; BORDER-LEFT: #1010ff 2px solid&quot;&gt;&lt;TT&gt;Wolfblade:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Th femme sat absolutely still for a moment.&nbsp; She was wanting to &lt;BR&gt;distance herself from that bot, but now her spark ached for his &lt;BR&gt;presense.&nbsp; She tried to remain calm and collected, but she finally &lt;BR&gt;broke down.&nbsp; She dropped he tools, and sobbed into her hands.&lt;BR&gt;&quot;Why... why did he go?&nbsp; Why did he go with them?&quot; she questioned &lt;BR&gt;outloud.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; : : Rodimus Prime/Kup : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Rodimus: She should be told, but perhaps by someone with a more &lt;BR&gt;softer edge. Kup, would you please tell her?&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Kup: You have to give me the heartwrenching jobs dont ya,&#39; lad. &lt;BR&gt;I&#39;ll take care of it though.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Kup heads to the science lab, walking in not long after Wolfblade.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Kup: Hello. There was more to tell
 you but I figure it would be &lt;BR&gt;better in private rather then up in that briefing room. I could tell &lt;BR&gt;that you care for Malice. I&#39;m sorry to tell you this, lass, but &lt;BR&gt;Malice was captured. He is now one of Unicron&#39;s Minions.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Kup looks down, his optics closeing with emotion. He couldn&#39;t look &lt;BR&gt;her streight in the optics. He had never liked telling bots bad news &lt;BR&gt;about their loved ones.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Yojinbo of Nightmare &lt;bustercross365@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Wolfblade/ Megatron Revived:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Wolfblade sighed heavy again.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &quot;Where did he go?&quot; she asked as she walked away.&nbsp; She returned to &lt;BR&gt;the &lt;BR&gt;&gt; lab and sat down on the bench.&nbsp; Someone wasn&#39;t talking.&nbsp; And who &lt;BR&gt;&gt; exactly was that big white bot?&nbsp; Things didn&#39;t seem right to her, &lt;BR&gt;but &lt;BR&gt;&gt; nonetheless, she continued working on the project.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Megatron watched the femme carefully, noted her body language, how &lt;BR&gt;&gt; she
 presented herself.&nbsp; She seemed to like Malice, like him a lot.&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; SHe tried to look annoyed, but he saw through her ruse.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &quot;Should I tell her?&nbsp; Should I tell her Malice was taken prisoner &lt;BR&gt;and &lt;BR&gt;&gt; is now a loyal minion?&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Rodimus: I&#39;m afraid I do not know the wherabouts of Malice. As &lt;BR&gt;for &lt;BR&gt;&gt; your plan, its interesting. A good idea. I should note that the &lt;BR&gt;&gt; possible instability of such a thing does worry me a bit, but in &lt;BR&gt;&gt; these times risks must be taken.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; robert riley &lt;bustercross365@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Wolfblade:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &quot;Oh!&nbsp; Yes sir!&nbsp; Malice and I decided that it might be a good idea &lt;BR&gt;&gt; to have a back plan to the cannon already in construction.&nbsp; We
 plan &lt;BR&gt;&gt; to use a high mass object and collapse it&#39;s gravity, turning it &lt;BR&gt;into &lt;BR&gt;&gt; a black hole.&nbsp; We wanted to launch it in an area of spatial &lt;BR&gt;&gt; instability.&nbsp; Once the black hole had served it&#39;s purpose, we &lt;BR&gt;planned &lt;BR&gt;&gt; to open a time rift and send it through.&nbsp; The rift should &lt;BR&gt;neutralize &lt;BR&gt;&gt; the intense gravity, expanding it to original size.&nbsp; In theory &lt;BR&gt;&gt; anyway.&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; The femme beamed at her explainatio, then a thought occured to &lt;BR&gt;her.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &quot;Where is Malice anyways?&nbsp; He went to do something, he said he&#39;d &lt;BR&gt;&gt; come back.&nbsp; hat was mega cycles ago!&nbsp; Where did he go?&quot; she asked, &lt;BR&gt;&gt; masking her concern with annoyance.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Rodimus: Thank you for reporting, Wolfblade. We were just curious &lt;BR&gt;&gt; as to what you have going on in the science lab. Could we
 possibly &lt;BR&gt;&gt; have a report on your activities?&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Yojinbo of Nightmare &lt;bustercross365@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Wolfblade:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Wolfblade was busy in the lab when Kup&#39;s call came through.&nbsp; She &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; sighed heavily and got up.&nbsp; She walked around their little &lt;BR&gt;science &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; project and made her to the conferance room.&nbsp; Inside was Kup and &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Rodimus, and a big white and black bot she had never seen &lt;BR&gt;before.&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; She looked warily at him, but turned to Kup and Rodimus.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &quot;Wolfblade reporting, per your orders.&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime/Kup : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus: That&#39;s Wolfblade. I dont know if she is still in the &lt;BR&gt;&gt; base. &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Kup?&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Kup
 shrugs.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Kup: With everything that has been happening lately I lost &lt;BR&gt;track &lt;BR&gt;&gt; of &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; who has been coming and going.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Kup hits a comm switch.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Kup: Wolfblade, this is Security Chief Kup. If you are still in &lt;BR&gt;&gt; the &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Maximal base, please report to the conference room per orders of &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Commander Rodimus Prime.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; robert riley &lt;bustercross365@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; OOC:&nbsp; Three or four I think.&nbsp; KitKat, Camoflage, Elita.&nbsp; I &lt;BR&gt;don&#39;t &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; know about the rest.&nbsp; The femme with Malice in the security tapes &lt;BR&gt;&gt; is &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Wolfblade, a femme from another dimention.&nbsp; She&#39;s a wolf if the &lt;BR&gt;&gt; name &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; doesn&#39;t clue into that.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; wrote: : : Rodimus
 Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus studies what they are doing. He knoes that the black &lt;BR&gt;hole &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; might work but would be unstable.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; He tries to recognize the femme.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; OOC: Let&#39;s see, how many fox femme&#39;s to we have? I&#39;m assuming &lt;BR&gt;its &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Nightlight but I dont want to post for it and be wrong. So who is &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; this fox femme?&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; robert riley &lt;bustercross365@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Megatron Revived:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; The Emperor clone watched several parts of the screen, until he &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; spotted Malice.&nbsp; He reached over and isolated the feed, the &lt;BR&gt;screen &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; changing to show just that one camera.&nbsp; It showed Malice and a &lt;BR&gt;wolf &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; femme working on something.&nbsp; Malice rolled some kind of sphere &lt;BR&gt;into &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; one of the
 labs and they installed something inside.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;That is an electro magnetic generator.&nbsp; This is perhaps a &lt;BR&gt;black &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; hole to be.&nbsp; I believe they plan to collapse it on itself, to &lt;BR&gt;&gt; create &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; an artifical black hole, to pull Unicron away from the planet.&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;But &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; what would they do to collapse it completely?&nbsp; Is this femme &lt;BR&gt;still &lt;BR&gt;&gt; in &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; the base?&nbsp; Perhaps she will clue us in as to what they were &lt;BR&gt;&gt; planning.&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus: I dont mind at all. I&#39;d like to look at them as well.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus hits a few controls on a computer panel, activating the &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; enarest screen. He pulls up the security logs and begins &lt;BR&gt;searching &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; them for Malice...&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;
 &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; robert riley &lt;bustercross365@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; OOC: I understand perfectly.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Megatron Revived:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;Then would you mind if I looked at the security camera files?&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;I &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; know he must have done something.&nbsp; He is too proud to sit idly &lt;BR&gt;and &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; wait on a plan.&nbsp; He must have come up some kind of back plan.&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Megatron was sure Malice did something before he was captured.&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; After all, he was a Decepticon, one of the Defenders of &lt;BR&gt;Cyberron.&nbsp; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; They were all resourceful and thinking ahead.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus: No, I&#39;m saying that we should go with the anti-Unicron &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; cannon as our respective plan &#39;a.&#39; The Decepticon
 Matrix should &lt;BR&gt;be &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; plan &#39;b.&#39;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus then turns to address Megatron&#39;s question about Malice.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus: As far as I know, all efforts are being directed &lt;BR&gt;towards &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; the connon construction.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; OOC: I&#39;m saying that because I&#39;m really not sure what Malice &lt;BR&gt;has &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; been doing during the time I was away from the RPG.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000 &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; Fortuneteller:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;The last resort????&quot;said the bot&quot;Are you telling that will you &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; search the autobot matrix of leadership?&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt;
